# Tailwind CSS v4 Design System

## How Tailwind v4 Works Here
- Config is CSS-first â€” defined in `app/globals.css` via `@theme {}`
- No `tailwind.config.js` file
- Import: `@import "tailwindcss";` at top of globals.css
- Custom token classes are auto-generated from `@theme` variables

## Color Token Reference

| Class | Color | Use |
|:------|:------|:----|
| `bg-bg-primary` | #0a0a0f | Page background |
| `bg-bg-secondary` | #12121a | Slightly lighter surface |
| `bg-bg-tertiary` | #1a1a27 | Cards, panels |
| `bg-glass` | rgba(255,255,255,0.06) | Glass card base |
| `border-glass-border` | rgba(255,255,255,0.1) | Glass borders |
| `text-text-primary` | #f0f0f5 | Main text |
| `text-text-secondary` | #a0a0b0 | Muted/caption text |
| `text-accent-blue` | #6366f1 | Primary accent |
| `text-accent-purple` | #8b5cf6 | Secondary accent |
| `text-accent-pink` | #ec4899 | Tertiary accent |
| `text-accent-cyan` | #22d3ee | Highlight |

