## Animation Keyframes Available
- `float` / `float-reverse` / `float-slow` â€” for background orbs
- `gradient-shift` â€” for animated gradients
- `pulse-glow` â€” subtle opacity pulse
- `fade-in-up` â€” entrance animation

## Usage Examples
```tsx
// Glass card
<div className="glass p-6 hover:border-glass-border-hover transition-colors">

// Gradient heading
<h2 className="gradient-text text-4xl font-bold">

// Section wrapper
<section id="about" className="section">

// Skill tag
<span className="tag">TypeScript</span>

// Gradient button
<button className="btn-gradient">View Work</button>

// Responsive grid
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
```

## Do NOT
- Use `style={{}}` inline styles
- Use arbitrary values when a token exists (e.g., don't use `bg-[#0a0a0f]`, use `bg-bg-primary`)
- Add custom CSS outside of `app/globals.css`
- Use `!important` overrides
